            <p class="card-text">Know about the different types of tickets AllCloud serves.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    </a>

    <a href="../Ticket" class="card-link">
    <div class="card">
     <img src="~/Images/employee.png" alt="Card image" class="card-img-top" />
